Major News Items in Leading Nigerian Newspapers
LAGOS , November 15 ( Xinhua ) -- Following are major news items in leading Nigerian newspapers Sunday .
New Nigerian :
-- The Nigerian government will take appropriate measures against those who stole from the nation 's coffers as soon as investigations are completed and all the money recovered , Head of State General Abdulsalam Abubakar disclosed in Lagos Saturday .
The Guardian :
-- Nigeria is to host Africa 's third field office of the United States of America 's Federal Bureau of Investigation .
The Post Express :
-- Nigeria 's presidential aspirant Chief Philip Asiodu returned Saturday from a three-week foreign trip with a warning that failure to enthrone a credible democratic government next year would spell doom for Nigeria .
